libucl
------------------------------------------
UCL is heavily infused by nginx configuration as the example of a convenient
configuration system.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.4.5-1
  libucl-devel-0.8.2-1bl1
  libucl5-0.8.2-1bl1
  pkg-config-1.9.4-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-1
  automake-11-1
  binutils-2.39-1
  cygport-0.36.0-1
  gcc-core-11.3.0-1
  gcc-g++-11.3.0-1
  libtool-2.4.7-1
  lua-5.3.6-4
  make-4.4-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/vstakhov/libucl

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/vstakhov/libucl/archive/refs/tags/0.8.2.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libucl-0.8.2-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libucl-0.8.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libucl-0.8.2-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libucl-0.8.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libucl5-0.8.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libucl-devel-0.8.2-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libucl)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libucl.README
  /usr/share/doc/libucl/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libucl/ChangeLog.md
  /usr/share/doc/libucl/README.md

(libucl5)
  /usr/bin/cygucl-5.dll

(libucl-devel)
  /usr/include/ucl++.h
  /usr/include/ucl.h
  /usr/lib/libucl.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libucl.pc
  /usr/share/man/man3/libucl.3.gz

